snippet.title: grepr - 7DFPS game full playthrough
snippet.description:
In Soviet Russia, bullet is you.

Created in seven days for the 2014 7DFPS challenge.

Built by Evan Todd - http://etodd.io
Audio by Jack Menhorn - http://jackmenhorn.com
Special thanks to the Unity Asset Store for several free models and textures and to Mixamo for the Sentinel model and animations.
